{"type": "article", "id": 38859, "title": "乐高推出积木胶带，以及，阿迪达斯春夏Lookbook不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-03-16T02:59:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1029, "name": "Lego"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 7973, "name": "Inditex"}, {"id": 8377, "name": "积木"}, {"id": 9287, "name": "Stan Smith"}, {"id": 10726, "name": "Dior Homme"}, {"id": 18579, "name": "OFF-WHITE"}, {"id": 2433, "name": "Cara Delevingne"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170316101728ce12yrW8dNm7jZFf.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.rttnews.com/2754723/guess-shares-down-10-on-weak-results.aspx\"><strong>Guess 发布第四季度财报，营收不及预期</strong></a> | 周三，Guess 发布第四季度财报，营收增长了 3.2%，至 6.793 亿美元，增长主要来自欧洲和亚洲市场。此外，Guess 的营收仍不及预期的 6.8598 亿美元，消息一出，Guess 的股价随之大跌了 10%。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/hm-revenues-up-q1-10844358/\"><strong>今年的第一季度，H&amp;M 营收上涨了 7%</strong></a> | H&amp;M 此前发布财报，显示该集团的营收在 2017 年的前三个月上涨 7%，至 60.2 亿美元。截止至 2 月 28 日，H&amp;M 在全球范围共有 4393 家店铺，去年同期为 3970 家。H&amp;M 去年的完整财报要在 3 月 30 日发布。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/business/2017/mar/15/zara-founder-payout-sales-amancio-ortega-inditex\"><strong>西班牙服饰零售集团 Inditex 去年净利润上涨了 10％</strong></a> | zara 的母公司，西班牙服饰零售集团 Inditex 发布财报，净利润上涨 10%，至 32 亿欧元。全球所有国家市场均得到了增长，销售额则上涨了 12%，突破 230 亿欧元。目前，Inditex 正在大力发展在线业务，去年新增门店 279 家，在 <a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/inditex-net-profit-up-2016-10844345/\">20 </a>个地区市场新上线了电商平台。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>继拍电影之后的又一个新动作，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/celebrities/celebrities-news/cara-delevingne-is-publishing-her-very-own-novel/\">超模 Cara Delevingne 要出书了</a>。Cara 在她的 Instagram 上公布，这本书名为《Mirror Mirror》，是她个人的首本小说，将在今年 10 月推出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102114zFgsKmpSxi4e8bBN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.10magazine.com/menswear/dior-homme-collaborate-with-japanese-artist-toru-kamei\">Dior Homme 最新一季，找来了日本艺术家龟井彻 Toru Kamei 合作</a>，把他的经典绣花搬到了西装、背包、衬衫和徽章上。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703161021298khfE10lCgX2T4rA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102129E8u52UTxjRLgw7fH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102139IFToQk62DsAxWmhe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102139HC3uSaOXhQo2gBzc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/03/15/adidas-highlights-ss17-collection/#slide-16\">阿迪达斯 2017 春夏系列</a>&nbsp;lookbook 发布，该系列的灵感来自 70 年代柏林流行的运动衫，丰富的色彩搭配和特殊剪裁，传递出了青春活力的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102151BkMXgKT4C6RJzqdU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102151DNj1sIZWMPaCXT5v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102151GpuJNQls5fqnU7yt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102151CB6juxMEXlkSivW4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703161021519HEV8GOkTlb4KZWs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102152MN5DjwAky8IiBq69.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102202iw0V37rCFZHguNo5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102202iA2JvfODBtE0WjdG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102203WkHw2utd1hvgKpbI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102202wl8cQjCn4xZs9yHb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102203qENAfDY8nX6tkQsy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102203gbGlZdC9etjaTI3O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017031610220386qYn1XFa3iKr9j4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102203ToGebYchyg8MfdI4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102204kH02a4UX5qxyKnlF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102203kuRHKh1D584i6TMS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102210cJph69OnNela2iYs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/03/15/adidas-stan-smith-boost-metallic-pack/#slide-5\">Stan Smith 推出了一个金属系列版本的</a>新系列，包括银色和玫瑰金两种色调。这个系列已经经由<a href=\"https://www.featuresneakerboutique.com/collections/adidas\"> feature </a>网站发售，售价为 120 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102220fxqVTzMpucvNaAtI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102232eJTE2iXWDbI0svdn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102232fv6t71UCR3oX0hBH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102237WfqkDYcP2njhsRVz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316102237WwGk5xbhja2JL1eI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>设计工作室 nimuno 与乐高合作，推出了一款<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/lego-tape-nimuno-loops-03-15-2017/\">“积木胶带”</a>。这种积木的背面有背胶，还可以灵活地变形、弯曲，甚至用剪刀剪裁，趣味性十足。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703161041588FOduRKc7Dge0QXb.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.392188\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316104157pouQ6WNMhUI4gcxZ.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.332813\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316104208QZsbjwEWGDBoK7T2.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.331250\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316104221tsY2ZTbFuW5U9gva.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316104221WwxhGMYOCi3tFIfT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.861858\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017031610422241aEBhbqYVLP0eK7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316104222dO0AQi1tglzcHw5F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316104239ER0NVDyCam1YXSqT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316104244gGoCOL6FBVRkQmat.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/03/15/off-white-nike-blazer-mid-closer-look/\">OFF-WHITE 与 Nike 的另一双联名款 Blazer Mid 曝光</a>。这双鞋的鞋身由白色皮革与灰色麂皮结合构成，鞋身上的巨大黑色 Nike 标志把橡胶中底和鞋身连接了起来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170316104304Qe5JwWLfBxpKzMXh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/03/15/adidas-stan-smith-boost-metallic-pack/#slide-5\">highsnobiety</a></p>"}